Daa-giin aabaji' daa-giishpin-andawendam dawaa ozhibii'an idan-wegonen-wabam onjida dagwagindan gagiibiingwe anishinaabewomin gaawesaa wabaam mazina'igan.

Wegonen-giin-idan daa-debise wiinawaa nisidotam onji-geye-mamizhim bindiig mazinaakizon geye mazinaatese. Gichi-apiitendaagwad ayaa gagiibiingwe anishinaabemowin geye anishinaabemowin aabajitoon agindan-mazinaatesijigan geye bagamaashi ikidowin-eta.
